            <h3 class="bds-sg-subtitle">Basic Pagination</h3>
            <p>This works for most instances. Be aware of the ARIA attributes here as they will help us identify the current page. By using the attribute <span class="inline-code">aria-current="true"</span> we can highlight the page the user is one while also maintaining Accessibility compliance.</p>

            <p>You can also shorten the pagination if there are too many pages or even use Previous / Next page options if the situation calls for it.</p>

            <div class="fieldset-demo">
                <nav class="pagination" role="navigation" aria-label="Pagination Navigation">
                    <ul class="list-pagination">
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Current Page, Page 1" aria-current="true">1</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 2">2</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 3">3</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 4">4</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <pre class="code-snippet">
                <code class="line-numbers">
                    <span>&lt;nav class="pagination" role="navigation" aria-label="Pagination Navigation"&gt;</span>
                        <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;ul class="list-pagination"&gt;</span>
                            <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" aria-label="Current Page, Page 1" aria-current="true"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span>
                            <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 2"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span>
                            <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 3"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span>
                            <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 4"&gt;4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span>
                        <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/ul&gt;</span>
                    <span>&lt;/nav&gt;</span>
                </code>
            </pre>

            <div class="fieldset-demo">
                <nav class="pagination" role="navigation" aria-label="Pagination Navigation">
                    <ul class="list-pagination">
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Previous Page">&laquo;</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 5">5</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 6">6</a></li>
