            <h3 class="bds-sg-subtitle">Advanced Pagination</h3>
            <p>For Data heavy Dashboards where you need more context, you can use the advanced pagination option. This one allows you to have more control over nagivation.</p>

            <div class="fieldset-demo">
                <nav class="pagination pagination-advanced" role="navigation" aria-label="Pagination Navigation">
                    <ul class="list-pagination">
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Previous Page">&laquo; Previous</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 5">5</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 6">6</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Current Page, Page 7" aria-current="true">7</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 8">8</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Page 9">9</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Goto Next Page">Next &raquo;</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="pagination-jump">
                        <input type="number" class="input input-tiny" value="7">
                        <span> of 140</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


